An internal link to `start <start>`__ and one to a
`page </some/namespace/page>`__ target.

A named internal link to `the start page <start>`__ guides the reader.

External links such as `Example <https://example.com>`__ and the bare
form https://example.org both work, as does an email like
user@example.com.

An interwiki shortcut points at
`Wiki <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki>`__ for background reading.
